      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "It seems you use IBM JVM. I&#39;ve never used it but found this parameter here (<a href=\"https://www-01.ibm.com/support/docview.wss?uid=swg21242497#Default_Settings_For_Dumps\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">www-01.ibm.com/support/&hellip;</a>). Please try to play with it:         -Xdump:java:defaults:file=dumps/%pid/javacore-%seq.txt  Try to change dumps/%pid/javacore-%seq.txt to your own path."
    } ],
